Name: View Invoices

Short Description: An Employee wishes to view a list of invoices.

Precondition: At least one Invoice exists.

Postcondition: A list of invoices has been viewed.

Error Condition: No invoice exists.

System state on error condition: No invoice is viewed.

Actors: Employee

Trigger: Employee wishes to view a list of invoices.

Standard procedure:
(1) Employee wishes to view invoices.
(2) Employee searches for invoices.
(3) Employee sees a list of invoices.

Alternate procedure:
(3') Employee is informed that no invoices exist. 